OL,3,CIndependent school may close in July
OL,4,Cif 'financial solution' isn't found
OL,6,FAn independent school in Berkshire
OL,7,Fsays it may be forced to close over
OL,8,Fits finances - leaving parents looking
OL,9,Ffor somewhere else to send their
OL,10,Fchildren.
OL,12,FSt Joseph's College in Upper Redlands
OL,13,FRoad in Reading says its unable to
OL,14,Ffind a secure financial future.
OL,16,FThe Independent School which offers
OL,17,Feducation to boys and girls from ages
OL,18,F3 to 18 has opened a consultation
OL,19,Fasking for suggestions on how to keep
OL,20,Fthe gates open.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/3
