OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1779379877
OL,3,CIndependent school may close in July
OL,4,Cif 'financial solution' isn't found
OL,6,FIf a solution isn't found - it said it
OL,7,Fwill shut at the end of term on the
OL,8,F10th of July.
OL,10,FIn a statement posted on the school's
OL,11,Fwebsite, Hilary Buckle said, "The
OL,12,FBoard has been looking at ways to
OL,13,Fensure the future of the school but it
OL,14,Fhas been unable to find a secure
OL,15,Ffinancial solution and therefore the
OL,16,Fconsultation will be asking staff for
OL,17,Fany suggestions they may have to keep
OL,18,Fthe school open and secure its future.
OL,20,F"If no solution is found, the school
OL,21,Fwill close on 10 July 2026."
OL,26,@sD@^OU}D@\O]
